data.description: Like new with gorgeous fixtures & finishes! Excellent Woodstock location near downtown in a gated community! Ideal floor plan combines the outdoor living into the main level with 3-panel glass doors leading to a spacious front porch. An abundance of natural light and high ceilings accentuate the open design of the entire home. Watch the family chef prepare meals in the gourmet kitchen equipped with a stainless steel gas range with a complementing wall vent, white shaker cabinets with savvy black hardware, a large prep island, beautiful quartz countertops, and a pantry. Open dining overlooks the family room with an electric fireplace. The upper level leads to a loft area for flex space, two secondary bedrooms with a full bath, and an Owner's retreat with spa-like appointments, including an oversized stepless & seamless glass shower, dual vanity with quartz countertops, and a large walk-in closet. Two-car garage with room for storage. Very neutral color palette waiting for your personalization. Located in an active community with a private gated entrance for peace of mind, a grand clubhouse with a fitness center, refreshing swimming pool, tennis/pickleball & bocce ball courts, a relaxing outdoor fire pit, and its own dog park where your four-legged companion can exercise. No rental restrictions. Approximately one mile to downtown Woodstock's GreenPrints parks & trails, boutiques, eateries, and arts!
